                                        <li>February Intake:</li>
                                        <li>Application Deadline: November to January (previous year)</li>
                                        <li>July Intake:</li>
                                        <li>Application Deadline: March to May</li>
                                        <li>October Intake:</li>
                                        <li>Application Deadline: June to August</li>
