                                    facilities.</li>
                                <li><strong>Food:</strong> Monthly food expenses can range from 500 to 800 MYR,
                                    depending on whether you cook at home or eat out.</li>
                                <li><strong>Transportation:</strong> Public transportation costs are relatively low in
                                    Malaysia. Monthly transportation expenses may range from 50 to 150 MYR, depending on
                                    your location and usage.</li>
                                <li><strong>Miscellaneous:</strong> Other miscellaneous expenses, including books,
